  <title>Week 9-10 Assignment</title>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <p>
        Calculate the mean and the standard deviation for this
        probability distribution on the domain <m>[1, \infty)</m>. (6)
      </p>
      <me>
        f(x) = \frac{3}{x^4} 
      </me>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Calculate the mean and the standard deviation for this
        probability distribution on the domain <m>[1,5]</m>. (6)
      </p>
      <me>
        f(x) = \frac{3(-x^2 + 6x -5)}{32} 
      </me>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Calculate the value of this series. (6)
      </p>
      <me>
        \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{2^n + 4^n}{16^n} 
      </me>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        Calculate the value of this series. (8) 
      </p>
      <me>
        \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{1}{(n+1)(n+4)}
      </me>
    </li>
  </ol>
